products.title: Legacy White 89mm Vertical Blind
products.description: The legacy blind is a beautiful, elegant and modern textured fabric which is available in a range of soft colours. This white vertical blind will add a fresh feel to any room in your home and will look great alongside existing neutral decor or as a contrast against darker tones. Product id: sdb-vtb0967 fabric colour: white material: 100% polyester headrail: white slimline headrail supported by white steel brackets - top or face fixable slat width: 89mm control type: smooth chain operation with cord tilt or wand tilt and pull energy saving rating: er2 - medium energy saving value - effective thermal retention light filtering: yes legacy white 89mm vertical blind in white.
